---
title: Spring Veggie Flatbread with Basil Pesto & Lemon
description: Lemon, squash, and basil pesto are a flavor combination we just couldn't keep to ourselves. Crispy flatbread and gooey mozzarella don't hurt the equation, either! A sprinkle of floral lemon zest on top wakes up the palate and reminds us that Spring is finally here!
